OL,3,CFootage released of Sussex ramraid as
OL,4,Cthieves target small jewellery store
OL,6,FThe owner of a small jewellery store
OL,7,Fin Bognor Regis has described how ram
OL,8,Fraiders ripped off his front window
OL,9,Fand stole tens of thousands of pounds
OL,10,Fworth of jewellery items.
OL,12,FTwo men smashed through shutters at
OL,13,FThe Arcade in the High Street in a
OL,14,Fstolen car before driving down the
OL,15,Fpedestrianised thoroughfare and
OL,16,Fbreaking into the independent business.
OL,18,FOwner Roger Clayden says #30,000,
OL,19,Fwhich is the equivalent of half of his
OL,20,Fstock, was stolen.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
