FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1772381500
OL,3,CFootage released of Sussex ramraid as
OL,4,Cthieves target small jewellery store
OL,6,FMr Clayden said: "I couldn't believe
OL,7,Fit when I saw the mess of all the
OL,8,Fbroken glass. It's just unbelievable.
OL,9,FThey broke all of the cabinets along
OL,10,Fthe side. All of these literally just
OL,11,Fsmashed the whole lot and the cabinet
OL,12,Fand grabbed everything out of it. And
OL,13,Fthe front door glass, it surprised me
OL,14,Fhow quickly that got broken."
OL,16,FFreddie Stevens, 22, of Gibbs Lane in
OL,17,FBordon in Hampshire was arrested and
OL,18,Fcharged with burglary and two counts
OL,19,Fof taking a motor vehicle without the
OL,20,Fowners' consent.
OL,26,@nD@ROUvD@]O]
