CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1772381500
OL,3,CFootage released of Sussex ramraid as
OL,4,Cthieves target small jewellery store
OL,6,FHe was jailed for two years.
OL,8,FThe court was told about how two Range
OL,9,FRovers were stolen in Yapton and
OL,10,FPulborough in the early hours of 11
OL,11,FNovember.
OL,13,FThe thieves forced entry into The
OL,14,FArcade via the High Street but damage
OL,15,Fwas also caused at the other entrance
OL,16,Fin Belmont Street.
OL,18,FImages showed a driver and one man who
OL,19,Fmatched Stevens' description taking
OL,20,Fapart shutters at the front of the
OL,21,Fjewellery shop inside.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
