OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1772381500
OL,3,CFootage released of Sussex ramraid as
OL,4,Cthieves target small jewellery store
OL,6,FAn alarm was activated at the
OL,7,Fjewellery store at 2.12am, and within
OL,8,Ffour minutes the vehicle had left the
OL,9,Farea.
OL,11,FThe damage caused to the shopping
OL,12,Fcentre meant all stores were closed
OL,13,Ffor two days for repairs to be made.
OL,15,FMr Clayden believes the stolen
OL,16,Fjewellery is long gone but is focusing
OL,17,Fhis efforts on rebuilding and
OL,18,Frepairing his shopfront, which is
OL,19,Fcurrently boarded up for safety
OL,20,Freasons.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1772381500
OL,3,CFootage released of Sussex ramraid as
OL,4,Cthieves target small jewellery store
OL,6,FHe's increasing security measures in
OL,7,Fhis shop and the arcade has also
OL,8,Femployed a security guard to more
OL,9,Fclosely monitor the parade of shops.
OL,11,FDistrict Commander Chief Inspector
OL,12,FAdam McCaig said: "This was a shocking
OL,13,Fincident that caused significant
OL,14,Fdisruption to businesses and the
OL,15,Fcommunity.
OL,17,F"Officers arrived within minutes, and
OL,18,Ffollowing a thorough investigation we
OL,19,Fwere able to identify one of the two
OL,20,Fsuspects as Freddie Stevens.
OL,26,@tD@SOUyD@AOU
