CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1772381500
OL,3,CFootage released of Sussex ramraid as
OL,4,Cthieves target small jewellery store
OL,6,F"I would like to thank businesses and
OL,7,Fthe public both for their patience and
OL,8,Falso for their support for our
OL,9,Finvestigation. Their help has ensured
OL,10,FStevens had no choice but to plead
OL,11,Fguilty when this matter went to court.
OL,12,FI am pleased he is now serving a
OL,13,Fcustodial sentence.
OL,15,F"Anyone with further information about
OL,16,Fthis incident can report it to Sussex
OL,17,FPolice online, quoting serial 71 of 11/
OL,18,F11/2026, or alternatively contact
OL,19,FCrimeStoppers anonymously on 0800 555
OL,20,F111."
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU|D@EO]
